race.comment: The feature of the day here and TALKANCO (15) takes on the older horses here after finishing strongly in the Breeders' Classic at Bunbury. Chris Parnham hops on board now and she's shown plenty of versatility in her early career. Right down in the weights and can make a statement second-up. ICE PICK NICK (12) finished off strongly in the Scenic Blast and looks primed out to 1300m here. He draws ideally for Steve Parnham and he's sure to be there at the finish. LONDON'S IMAGE (4) stuck on well in the Cyril Flower and can improve with that run under her belt. ELITE MISSILE (9) was impressive fresh and has been kept up to the mark with a recent trial. Include.
